TITLE: Setting Up Request Interceptor for Axios
DESCRIPTION: This snippet shows how to set up a request interceptor in Axios that initializes a new HTTP metric for performance monitoring before the request is sent out. It uses the Firebase Performance Monitoring library to track metrics, including request URL and method. The `httpMetric` is attached to the request's metadata for later use when processing the response.
