TITLE: Setting Up Response Interceptor for Axios
DESCRIPTION: This snippet demonstrates how to implement a response interceptor in Axios to manage both successful and failed requests. The interceptor updates the HTTP metric with the response data, such as status code and content type, ensuring that all performance data is logged for both successful and failed requests. It also ensures that errors are properly propagated after logging.
